To a silent warrior: I have long been a student of the I ching and Sun Tsu, and both continue to teach me the wisdom of war and peace.  And that changes must continue.<br><br>
Arthur: I truly do not understand your anger at me. I thought the issue was between Ed and I, so why it is &quot;unacceptible&quot; to you is puzzling. Do you not want divergent viewpoints to communicate?  You are a smart man, and I am sure that you have fallen prey to your emotions, God I know that one well. I look foward to your post when you regroup, and I thank you for giving me the opportunity to do the same, I sure needed it. Arthur, we have worlds yet to discover, yet to discuss, disagree, fight, and reconcile over. Don't quit on me now.<br><br>
doc spatz
